{"word":"διαγκυλίζομαι","slug":"διαγκυλίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαγκυλίζομαι</b></el> <el><b>δι-αγκυλόομαι</b></el> <el><b>δι-αγκυλωμένος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀγκύλη'><el>ἀγκύλη</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to hold a javelin by the thong</i><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>διηγκυλισμένος</el>, of a man, <i>ready to shoot</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—so (from <el>di-agkulo/omai</el>), <el>διηγκυλωμένος</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}